main event: A witness observed a slow-moving object in the sky with a pulsating red light in Moorestown, New Jersey.
interesting points: The object was initially thought to be an aircraft but could not be confirmed as such.,The slowly moving object was visible for about 30 seconds.,Several witnesses observed the same object at different times.,The object's appearance was described as having a strange metallic look.,The witness reported the sighting to the police shortly after it occurred.
sighted object: a slow-moving object with a pulsating red light
